videos.description: Dwayne Sutton shows no hesitation as he knocks down a deep 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: Louisville's Sutton sinks 3-ball from NBA range

videos.description: Foster Loyer takes advantage of the open lane for a bank shot to put No. 9 Michigan State ahead of Louisville.
videos.headline: Loyer drives baseline for Michigan State bucket

videos.description: Michigan State's Kenny Goins can't knock down a potential game winning free throw and Louisville is forced into a bad shot to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Michigan State-Louisville heads to OT after ugly sequence
